<figcaption data-index="651"><p data-index="652"><span class="figureLabel" data-index="653"><b data-index="654"><a role="doc-backlink" href="#c19-fig-8-1" data-index="655" data-section-index="29" data-section-idref="c19-fig-8-1" data-target-data-index="586"><span style=" background-color: #226C7B; color: #FFFFFF;" data-index="656">ILLUSTRATION 19.8</span></a></b> <b data-index="657">Schedule of Future Taxable Amounts</b></span></p></figcaption>
