<p data-index="658">Because it is the first year of operations for Chelsea, there is no deferred tax liability at the beginning of the year. Chelsea computes the income tax expense for 2020 as shown in <a class="blue" href="#c19-fig-9" id="c19-fig-9-1" data-index="659" data-section-index="29" data-section-idref="c19-fig-9" data-target-data-index="661"><b data-index="660">Illustration 19.9</b></a>.</p>
