<p data-index="1475">At the end of 2021 (the second year), the difference between the book value and the tax basis of the litigation liability is zero. Therefore, there is no deferred tax asset at this date. Assuming that income taxes payable for 2021 is $90,000, Hunt computes income tax expense for 2021 as shown in <a class="blue" href="#c19-fig-22" id="c19-fig-22-1" data-index="1476" data-section-index="29" data-section-idref="c19-fig-22" data-target-data-index="1478"><b data-index="1477">Illustration 19.22</b></a>.</p>
