<p data-index="2809"><span epub:type="pagebreak" role="doc-pagebreak" title="19-18" id="Page_19-18" data-index="2810"></span>Hostel, therefore, recognizes the decrease of $400,000 ($1,200,000 – $800,000) at the end of 2020 in the deferred tax liability as follows.</p>
<table style=" width: 60%;" data-index="2811">
