</div>
<figcaption data-index="3194"><p data-index="3195"><span class="figureLabel" data-index="3196"><b data-index="3197"><a role="doc-backlink" href="#c19-fig-37-1" data-index="3198" data-section-index="29" data-section-idref="c19-fig-37-1" data-target-data-index="3141"><span style=" background-color: #226C7B; color: #FFFFFF;" data-index="3199">ILLUSTRATION 19.37</span></a></b> <b data-index="3200">Recognition of the Benefit of the Loss Carryforward in the Loss Year</b></span></p></figcaption>
