</tbody></table>
<figcaption data-index="5177"><p data-index="5178"><span class="figureLabel" data-index="5179"><b data-index="5180"><a role="doc-backlink" href="#c19A-fig-2-1" data-index="5181" data-section-index="29" data-section-idref="c19A-fig-2-1" data-target-data-index="5157"><span style=" background-color: #226C7B; color: #FFFFFF;" data-index="5182">ILLUSTRATION 19A.2</span></a></b> <b data-index="5183">Computation of Income Taxes Payable, End of 2019</b></span></p></figcaption>
</figure>
</section>
