<section id="c19-sec-0022" data-index="5562">
<h3 data-index="5563"><span class="red" data-index="5564">Financial Statement Presentation—2019</span></h3>
<p data-index="5565">Companies should classify deferred tax assets and liabilities as noncurrent on the balance sheet. Multiple categories of deferred taxes are classified into a net noncurrent amount. <a class="blue" href="#c19A-fig-8" id="c19A-fig-8-1" data-index="5566" data-section-index="29" data-section-idref="c19A-fig-8" data-target-data-index="5568"><b data-index="5567">Illustration 19A.8</b></a> shows the classification of Allman's deferred tax accounts at the end of 2019.</p>
<figure id="c19A-fig-8" data-index="5568">
<div style=" background-color: #FFFDE5; padding: 0.3em; border: 1px solid #000;" data-index="5569">
<table style=" width: 50%;" data-index="5570">
<tbody data-index="5571">
<tr data-index="5572">
<td data-index="5573"></td>
<td colspan="2" data-index="5574"><span class="right" data-index="5575"><span class="bdr1" data-index="5576">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Resulting Deferred Tax&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></td>
</tr>
<tr data-index="5577">
<td data-index="5578"><span class="bdr1" data-index="5579">Temporary Difference</span></td>
