<p class="latin1" data-index="5762"><span class="label" data-index="5763"><b data-index="5764">5.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> 	During 2020, nontaxable municipal bond interest revenue was $24,000.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="5765"><span class="label" data-index="5766"><b data-index="5767">6.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> 	Allman accrued a loss of $172,000 for financial reporting purposes because of pending litigation. This amount is not tax-deductible until the period the loss is realized, which the company estimates to be 2028.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="5768"><span class="label" data-index="5769"><b data-index="5770">7.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> 	Pretax financial income for 2020 amounts to $504,800.</p>
