<p data-index="7195"><b data-index="7196">e.</b></p>
<p data-index="7197"><span class="center" data-index="7198"><b data-index="7199">2021</b></span></p>
<table style=" width: 60%;" data-index="7200">
<tbody data-index="7201">
<tr data-index="7202">
<td data-index="7203">Deferred Tax Asset*</td>
<td data-index="7204"><div class="right" data-index="7205">8,980</div></td>
<td data-index="7206"></td>
</tr>
<tr data-index="7207">
<td data-index="7208"><span class="hidden" data-index="7209">00</span>Income Tax Expense (Loss Carryforward)</td>
<td data-index="7210"></td>
<td data-index="7211"><div class="right" data-index="7212">8,980</div></td>
</tr>
<tr data-index="7213">
<td colspan="3" data-index="7214">*Carryforward ($44,900 × 20 = $8,980 deferred tax asset)</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p class="extract" data-index="7215">No valuation allowance is needed since Johnny Bravo is expected to return to profitability in 2022. This is positive evidence that the deferred tax asset will be realized.</p>
