<p id="c19-ex-0019" data-index="7544"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="7545"><b data-index="7546">E19.3</b></span> <b class="red" data-index="7547">(LO <a href="c19.xhtml#lo_1" data-index="7548" data-section-index="29" data-section-idref="lo_1" data-target-data-index="87"><b class="red" data-index="7549">1</b></a>, <a href="c19.xhtml#lo_2" data-index="7550" data-section-index="29" data-section-idref="lo_2" data-target-data-index="1838"><b class="red" data-index="7551">2</b></a>)</b> <img style=" vertical-align: middle;" src="https://ereader-books-prod.chegg.com/682/9781119503682/39c53495-be04-40a4-af01-80a39a7df223/OPS/images/excel.jpg" alt="An icon reading text, “Excel”" data-index="7552" data-size="%7B%22width%22%3A46%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D"> <b data-index="7553">(One Temporary Difference, Future Taxable Amounts, One Rate, Beginning Deferred Taxes)</b> Bandung Corporation began 2020 with a $46,000 balance in the ­Deferred Tax Liability account. At the end of 2020, the related cumulative temporary difference amounts to $350,000, and it will reverse evenly over the next 2 years. Pretax accounting income for 2020 is $525,000, the tax rate for all years is 20%, and taxable income for 2020 is $405,000.</p>
