<p class="latin1" data-index="7559"><span class="label" data-index="7560"><b data-index="7561">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Prepare the journal entry to record income tax expense, deferred income taxes, and income taxes payable for 2020.</p>
