<p class="latin1" data-index="7882"><span class="label" data-index="7883"><b data-index="7884">1.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> <span class="Times" data-index="7885"> Deferred tax liability, January 1, 2020, $30,000.</span></p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="7886"><span class="label" data-index="7887"><b data-index="7888">2.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> <span class="Times" data-index="7889"> Deferred tax asset, January 1, 2020, $10,000.</span></p>
