<h4 data-index="9051"><span class="red" data-index="9052">Instructions</span></h4>
<p data-index="9053">Prepare the journal entries for the years 2017 to 2021 to record income tax expense and the effects of the net operating loss carrybacks and carryforwards assuming Dan Lynch Company uses the carryback provision. All income and losses relate to normal operations. (In recording the benefits of a loss carryforward, assume that no valuation account is deemed necessary.)</p>
