<h4 data-index="9656"><span class="red" data-index="9657">Instructions</span></h4>
<p class="latin1" data-index="9658"><span class="label" data-index="9659"><b data-index="9660">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Prepare the journal entries to record the income tax expense, deferred income taxes, and the income taxes payable at the end of each year. No deferred income taxes existed at the beginning of <span class="Arial" data-index="9661">2020</span>.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="9662"><span class="label" data-index="9663"><b data-index="9664">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Explain how the deferred taxes will appear on the balance sheet at the end of each year. </p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="9665"><span class="label" data-index="9666"><b data-index="9667">c.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Draft the income tax expense section of the income statement for each year, beginning with “Income before income taxes.”</p>
<p id="c19-ex-0051" data-index="9668"><span epub:type="pagebreak" role="doc-pagebreak" title="19-55" id="Page_19-55" data-index="9669"></span><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="9670"><b data-index="9671">P19.8</b></span> <b class="red" data-index="9672">(LO</b> <a href="c19.xhtml#lo_1" data-index="9673" data-section-index="29" data-section-idref="lo_1" data-target-data-index="87"><b class="red" data-index="9674">1</b></a>, <a href="c19.xhtml#lo_2" data-index="9675" data-section-index="29" data-section-idref="lo_2" data-target-data-index="1838"><b class="red" data-index="9676">2</b></a>, <a href="c19.xhtml#lo_4" data-index="9677" data-section-index="29" data-section-idref="lo_4" data-target-data-index="3749"><b class="red" data-index="9678">4</b></a><span class="red" data-index="9679">)</span> <b data-index="9680">(Two Differences, 2 Years, Compute Taxable Income and Pretax Financial Income)</b> The following information was disclosed during the audit of Elbert Inc.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="9681"><span class="label" data-index="9682"><b data-index="9683">1.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> </p>
<table style=" width: 40%;" data-index="9684">
