<p id="c19-ex-0060" data-index="10284"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="10285"><b data-index="10286">CE19.1</b></span> Access the glossary (“Master Glossary”) to answer the following.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="10287"><span class="label" data-index="10288"><b data-index="10289">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> What is a deferred tax asset?</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="10290"><span class="label" data-index="10291"><b data-index="10292">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> What is taxable income?</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="10293"><span class="label" data-index="10294"><b data-index="10295">c.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> What is the definition of valuation allowance?</p>
